  "title": "Safety Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Conduct safety and health inspections to eliminate unsafe acts, conditions, and occupational risks in the workplace.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Recommend practicable measure, document and report infringements, including photographic evidence, to management and relevant personnel.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Implement and monitor risk control measures effectively.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Ensure compliance with Singapore Civil Defence Force Fire Safety Bureau regulations by carrying out fire hazard inspections within the premises.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Develop and review safe work procedures and Risk Assessments.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Assist in preparing and submitting safety and health documents to relevant authorities.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Investigate workplace incidents involving employees, prepare preliminary reports, and support work injury compensation claims and reporting.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Conduct Workplace Safety and Health Committee meetings and prepare meeting minutes.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Arrange necessary safety and health orientation courses and related training for workers.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Enhance safety awareness by organizing promotional activities such as safety posters, bulletin boards, videos, and exhibitions.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Conduct safety training sessions to improve workers’ safety consciousness and knowledge.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Maintain and update ISO and BizSAFE documentation.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>At least 5 years of relevant experience in safety coordination.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Possess qualifications recognized by MOM.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>MOM-registered Workplace Safety and Health Officer (WSHO).</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Completed Fire Safety Manager (FSM) course.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Trained in EHS management systems, such as ISO 45001, ISO 14001, and ISO 9001.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Strong knowledge of MOM regulations.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Proficient in computer applications.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>A team player who is results-oriented, independent, and possesses good coordination skills.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Please include the following information in your resume:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Personal particulars.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Educational background.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Work experience (detailed in point form).</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Reasons for leaving previous roles.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Current and expected salary.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Availability or notice period.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>",
